TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Radar can't see underwater - for that you need sonar.
You can produce resources in the sea.

TriggerLogic.Name: GUI Message
TriggerLogic.Message: As well as vehicles and kbots, you can make sea and air units. Learn about the different types of ship and plane in this mission. Your objective is to find and destroy the enemy units, which are scattered across the map.

TriggerLogic.Name: Marker
TriggerLogic.Text: Press "l" to discover how far your radar sees.
